{"tid":2110194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保安局：對正常培訓活動因政治因素被暫停感遺憾","createTime":"2020-07-15T17:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T01:13:02.000Z","uid":7542,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"79aab136e769d9c6cc05a042d8b97fa44361ce7a","tid":2110194,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T17:40:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">保安局可唔可以反制<br />\n中止返香港訓練美國警察嘅活動<br />\n唔好一句遺憾就算 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HD4VDn3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHD4VDn3.jpg&h=d5fc154c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fN5YA9J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfN5YA9J.png&h=df9983c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保安局回應美國簽署《香港自治法案》，指香港紀律部隊一直與世界各地培訓夥伴，維持廣泛的合作關係，對於正常的培訓活動因政治因素被暫停，表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，特區政府强烈譴責外國政府，因政治因素而對香港作出的種種所謂制裁，這些措施是政治操作和政治表態，沒有客觀的事實基礎。紀律部隊會繼續安排合適的培訓交流機會，以提升執法效率及服務質素。<br />\n<br />\n美國簽署《香港自治法案》及一項行政命令，措施包括取消對香港的優惠待遇、制裁將來執行國安法的官員，以及結束向香港警隊或其他香港安全部門提供培訓等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537999-20200716.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537999-20200716.htm&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n384e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=7f60c01b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1537999-20200716.htm&h=f2a98591\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1537999-20200716.htm</a>"},{"pid":"980d8485ceb23aa29cfe3034edb39e61c205e108","tid":2110194,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T17:42:08.000Z","msg":"<strong>又話說，唔知香港國安警察係接受邊個嘅訓練呢？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FF-SKS89xxRg&d=CgM6%2BPDcwTI4Uk%2BisK9n384e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=a5ca70f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/F-SKS89xxRg</a>"},{"pid":"59fb49448ca7dacae28a243ab6212f013da49723","tid":2110194,"uid":208227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-15T17:45:51.000Z","msg":"一直以來由外國勢力去培訓，愛國嘅我感到好遺憾。這是撥亂反正好機會，保安局同志，我希望你能好好反思一下。"},{"pid":"0692d820f94dc5fc0be8c7c830f340aebb759aaf","tid":2110194,"uid":328494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T01:13:02.000Z","msg":"人地外國勢力有責任一定要培訓你？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}